descriptionHtml:
Adds a pair of black high heel Mary-Janes to the game. They come with separately equippable little lace socks. Shoe and sock meshes and textures are completely custom. Requires NetImmerse Override for the heels. If you have RaceMenu you already have this. Otherwise you can get it separately here [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/37481]https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/37481[/url]. The socks only work with these shoes. To obtain the items use "help Babydoll" for the shoes and "help sock" for the socks in the console. or get the Additem Menu mod [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/64905]https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/64905[/url].

I have made 2 versions that will fit the majority UNP/UUNP and CBBE bodies without gap or texture seam. If you have an ankle gap, you should consider switching to a body that hasn't had the ankle size altered.

There is a separate .esp in the misc section that will add High Heel sound to the shoes. You need to visit Loverslab and download and install the Heel Sound mod https://www.loverslab.com/files/file/1795-heels-sound/  first, or this will crash your game.
